<p>I'm using the Gradle Maven plugin and I'm used to see the location of the generated Jars when using Maven.</p>  <p>How to print the location of the Maven dependency after the build finishes... Something like this:</p>  <pre><code>$ gradle clean install:clean :compileJava :processResources :classes :jar :install Installed at /home/mdesales/.m2/repository/com/x/platform/listeners/x-asynclistener/1.0.0/x-asynclistener-1.0.0.jar  BUILD SUCCESSFUL  Total time: 4.181 secs </code></pre>